description:
Easy way to add your Landbot livechat to your page.
I've done it for myself, why not letting everyone benefit from it! :)

DEMO : https://joapp-demo01.bubbleapps.io/version-test/landbot

If you have specific requests feel free to fill this form : https://joapp.ca/request
name: Landbot
plugin_instructions:
1 - Create a Landbot account

2 - Create a bot

3 - In your bot, go to the "share" tab, on this page you should see a code sample. Search inside where its written "configUrl". It should look something similar to this : 'https://chats.landbot.io/v3/YOUR_UNIQUE_CODE/index.json'

5 - Copy the whole URL without the
quotation marks and paste it in your plugin page. 

You're ready to go!
